lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Marilyn Manson, Antichrist Superstar
In the glare of fame, a cosmic avatar
He dances with shadows, he plays with fire
A dark enigma, a twisted desire

(Chorus)
Antichrist superstar, a figure of fright
With lyrics like daggers, cutting through the night
He wears his darkness like a crown
In a world where madness is renowned

(Verse 2)
Born of rebellion, a creature of sin
He dares to challenge the world we're in
With makeup and mayhem, he crafts his art
A masterpiece of chaos tearing us apart

(Chorus)
Antichrist superstar, a figure of fright
With lyrics like daggers, cutting through the night
